data.description: This home features 3 bedrooms and 3 baths. As you enter the home you will be in the formal living/sitting room.  Two bedrooms have ensuite bathrooms.  This home has a large kitchen with a counter you can cozy up to on the bar stools.  Kitchen opens up to the den that has a  beautiful fireplace.  New carpet in bedrooms. Wood laminate and tile throughout the remaining rooms.  Relax after a long day on your porch/Arizona room with the beautiful mountain views.  Ample parking on property with room to park an RV.  3 car garage with the ability to park 3 additional in driveway.  Large storage shed on property. Great opportunity to live in a wonderful Prescott Valley neighborhood without an HOA.
